description.desc: Increases the potency of Flamethrower and Ice Splitter.
description.name: Elemental Boost

description.desc: An additional octopus is summoned, increasing the fire rate and the damage.\nRequired Skill : #cLevel 30 of Octopus#
description.name: Wrath of the Octopi

description.desc: Applies more damage to monsters under the effect of Homing Beacon.\nRequired Skill : #cLevel 30 of Homing Beacon#
description.name: Bullseye

description.desc: 일정 시간 동안 파티원의 모든 스탯을 일정 퍼센트 올려 준다.
description.name: 메이플 용사

description.desc: Uses the grenade attack of Gaviota to damage up to 6 monsters. \nRequired Skill : #cLevel 15 of Gaviota#
description.name: Aerial Strike

description.desc: Fires rounds of bullets very quickly. Hold on to the skill key for continued shooting.\nRequired Skill : #cLevel 20 of Burst Fire#
description.name: Rapid Fire

description.desc: Calls forth a ship that you can mount and launch attacks from. The durability of the ship decreases per damage received, and when it reaches 0, you will not be able to get back on board for a short period of time. \nAvailable Skills : Battleship skills, Grenades, Gun Booster, Flamethower.
description.name: Battleship

description.desc: Rapidly fires a number of cannonballs. Only available when aboard the Battleship.\nRequired Skill : #cLevel 1 of Battleship#
description.name: Battleship Cannon

description.desc: Fires a hardened cannonball that goes through monsters. Only available when aboard the Battleship.\nRequired Skill : #cLevel 1 of Battleship#
description.name: Battleship Torpedo

description.desc: Hypnotizes monsters to temporarily make it attack other monsters instead of you.
description.name: Hypnotize

description.desc: Uses HP and MP to temporarily increase the attacking speed of a weapon. This can be combined with other boosters, and everyone in the party will be positively affected by this.\nRequired Skill : #cLevel 20 of Knuckler Booster#
description.name: Speed Infusion
